                                jcr:primaryType="nt:unstructured"
                                sling:resourceType="abbvie-com2/components/text/v2/text"
                                text="&lt;p>&lt;br>&#xd;&#xa;Everything we all do at AbbVie is grounded in &lt;a href=&quot;/content/abbvie-com2/us/en/who-we-are/our-principles.html&quot;>our Principles&lt;/a>. These commitments have helped our company make a remarkable impact since our founding in 2013 – transforming lives, acting with integrity, driving innovation, serving the community and embracing diversity &amp;amp; inclusion.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>Inclusion shapes the way we lead. It connects us to possibilities we wouldn’t otherwise see. And, it unlocks a level of performance and growth we couldn’t otherwise achieve.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;&lt;p>We are proud to offer an environment that allows our colleagues around the world to achieve their full potential. When everyone can be themselves at work and when they’re treated with respect and dignity, we maximize every employee’s potential. By unlocking the exponential potential found in each person, we strengthen the entire business.&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
                                textIsRich="true"/>
                        </par_12>
